OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1776967870
OL,3,CSara Cox to replace Scott Mills on BBC
OL,4,CRadio 2 Breakfast Show
OL,6,FSara Cox will replace Scott Mills on
OL,7,Fthe BBC Radio 2 Breakfast Show, the
OL,8,Fbroadcaster has announced.
OL,10,FThe DJ, who currently hosts the
OL,11,Fstation's weekday Teatime show, will
OL,12,Flaunch her first show this summer, the
OL,13,FBBC said in a statement.
OL,15,F"There are not enough adjectives to
OL,16,Freally sum up how I'm feeling about
OL,17,Fbeing trusted with such an iconic
OL,18,Fshow, but let's start with ecstatic,
OL,19,Fhonoured and incredibly chuffed," Cox
OL,20,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
