OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1776967870
OL,3,CSara Cox to replace Scott Mills on BBC
OL,4,CRadio 2 Breakfast Show
OL,6,F"I've had the most glorious seven
OL,7,Fyears of my career on Teatime so thank
OL,8,Fyou to my brilliant Teatime listeners
OL,9,Fwho hopefully will join me at
OL,10,FBreakfast for excellent music and all
OL,11,Fmy usual nonsense plus some superstar
OL,12,Fguests.
OL,14,F"I honestly can't wait to wake the
OL,15,Fnation up with the biggest, most fun
OL,16,Fbreakfast show ever."
OL,18,FCox will replace Mills, who was sacked
OL,19,Fby the BBC in March over allegations
OL,20,Frelating to "personal conduct".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
