PN,30704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1776967870
OL,3,CSara Cox to replace Scott Mills on BBC
OL,4,CRadio 2 Breakfast Show
OL,6,FThe BBC announced his departure before
OL,7,Fit emerged that the Metropolitan
OL,8,FPolice had launched an investigation
OL,9,Finto the 53-year-old in 2016 over
OL,10,Fallegations of serious sexual offences
OL,11,Finvolving a teenage boy under 16
OL,12,Fbetween 1997 and 2000.
OL,14,FThe investigation, which Mills said he
OL,15,Ffully co-operated with in 2018, did
OL,16,Fnot result in any criminal charges
OL,17,Fafter the Crown Prosecution Service
OL,18,Fdetermined there was insufficient
OL,19,Fevidence.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
