PN,30705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1776967870
OL,3,CSara Cox to replace Scott Mills on BBC
OL,4,CRadio 2 Breakfast Show
OL,6,FHe said in a statement: "Since the
OL,7,Finvestigation related to an allegation
OL,8,Fthat dates back nearly 30 years and
OL,9,Fthe police investigation was closed 7
OL,10,Fyears ago, I hope that the public and
OL,11,Fthe media will understand and respect
OL,12,Fmy wish not to make any further public
OL,13,Fcomment on this matter."
OL,15,FGary Davies has been filling in as
OL,16,Fbreakfast show host since Mills was
OL,17,Ftaken off the air.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
