OL,3,CSara Cox to replace Scott Mills on BBC
OL,4,CRadio 2 Breakfast Show
OL,6,FCox joined BBC Radio 1 in 1999 to
OL,7,Fpresent a Saturday lunchtime show,
OL,8,Fbefore moving on the following year to
OL,9,Fpresent the Radio 1 Breakfast Show
OL,10,Funtil December 2003.
OL,12,FOver the following 11 years, she has
OL,13,Fpresented various shows on the
OL,14,Fnetwork, including the weekday
OL,15,Fafternoon show, a weekend afternoon
OL,16,Fshow and weekday mornings.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
