PN,30707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1776967870
OL,3,CSara Cox to replace Scott Mills on BBC
OL,4,CRadio 2 Breakfast Show
OL,6,FShe joined Radio 2 in 2011, deputising
OL,7,Ffor various presenters across the
OL,8,Fschedule and moving to host the
OL,9,FTeatime show in 2018. The show was
OL,10,Fextended from two hours to three hours
OL,11,Fin 2022.
OL,13,F"Sara is adored by her millions of
OL,14,Flisteners at Teatime, and having
OL,15,Fregularly deputised in the slot, I
OL,16,Falready know she'll build a brilliant
OL,17,Frapport with the Breakfast audience
OL,18,Fand get the nation going each morning
OL,19,Fwith her trademark warmth and humour,"
OL,20,Fsaid Helen Thomas, Head of Radio 2.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
